content:
It was really great,this has to be the best baseball anime with Chracter Development.
Cons:- It felt really rushed towards the end. It would be better to get an after story kind of 2-3 episode  OVA.
At the time of writing this, how many episodes of Cross Game have you seen?
Note: This area is only to be used for posting a review of the series after you have seen it. This is not a discussion area.
